import { Box, Grid, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

const skils = ["react", "node", "js"]

const JobCard = () => {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item xs>
                    <Typography variant="subtitle1" >Need React Dev</Typography>
                    <Typography variant="subtitle2" >Google</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item container xs>
                    {
                        skils.map((skil) => (
                            <Grid item key={skil}>
                                {skil}
                            </Grid>
                        ))
                    }
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs>
                    <Typography variant="caption">22 min ago</Typography>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default JobCard
